text: Ethel Ida Sanborn (1883-1952) was an American paleobotanist and professor of botany at Oregon State College and University of Oregon. She published extensively on the flora of Oregon and the Western United States. == Works == * * * * * * ==References== Category:1883 births Category:1952 deaths Category:American women scientists Category:American botanists Category:Paleobotanists
